title: Chicken Invaders 5: Cluck of the Dark Side [FINAL] 2014 (PC) Fox
description:
About Game:
************
Chicken Invaders puts you at the forefront of a battle against invading intergalactic chickens, bent on revenge against the human race for our oppression of Earth chickens. In this episode, the chickens have hatched a devious plan to block out sunlight and freeze Earth to death. It's up to you to travel around the galaxy in order to piece together an ancient artifact and (quite literally) save the day. 

Game Features:
**************
-Finger-blistering shooting action with over 200 chickens on-screen simultaneously
-Gigantic boss fights
-Eggceptional graphics
-Journey to 12 intergalactic star systems
-All the fried chicken you can eat!
-Fly planetary missions on strange and wonderful alien worlds
-Eggcellent comentary
-Fight through 120 waves of invading chickens

**TESTED ON WINDOWS 8.1 & TOUCHSCREEN COMPATIBLE**

Game Info:
***********
Ready 2 Play
Crack: Velocity/RAZZ
RePacked by: Foxy Games
Released: December 2014
Size: 50 Mb
Platform: PC / Windows

About Update:
**************
This update includes a further fix for the issue of after giving the first part of the crown to the mermaid, the clippers disappear. Once installed you'll be able to continue your existing game.

Instructions:
**************
1.Download
2.Install
3.Play and Have Fun 
4.Keep Seeding!
